settings.description: Use the POW block to clear rows of enemies while solving puzzles in this watery ghost house.
I didn't actually create this level, a relative did.
To carry a flurry, press the run button when above it on a semisolid. Can be used in Freezeflame Manor.
Chargin' Chucks lead their fellow Bob-ombs into this tight, grassy water filled course.
Flutters fly across the sky and Wigglers are bound on ground in this simple nighttime course.
It's all just Tetriminos in this wacky world.

Ultra Star-esque Fast Parabeetle Platforming.
NOTE FOR SECTION 2: You can walk off a ledge and jump in midair with the kuribo's shoe.
In this field, Fireflowers grow naturally out of the floor, how convenient!
Galoombas walk around in their peaceful hills, with lots of sandy and thin structures.
If you don't make it, you warp right back to try again.
